# Nearest Police Station Alert System

This report describes the architecture, implementation, and integration of the **Nearest Police Station Alert System** into the **AI Command Center for Bengaluru Traffic Police** project for the Flipkart Gridlock Hackathon.

---

## 1. System Architecture

The Nearest Police Station Alert System locates the closest responder station from incident coordinates using the Haversine distance formula, evaluates availability, plots a dispatch map, compiles a structured incident alert, and simulates SMS gateway transmission.

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Incident Coordinates] --> B[PoliceStationFinder]
    B -->|Load police_station.csv| C[Calculate Proximity]
    C -->|Haversine Formula| D[Identify Nearest Station & ETA]
    D --> E[Check Officer Availability]
    E --> F[Generate Alert Text]
    F --> G[Simulate SMS Gateway Dispatch]
```

